org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web.workload

Interface IWorkloadGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PeriodTimeGenerator, PeriodWorkloadGenerator, RandomIPWorkloadGenerator, StatWorkloadGenerator

    public interface IWorkloadGenerator
    Represents a timed factory for sessions of a given type. Defines the workload consisting of sessions of a given type directed to a data center.
    Author:
    nikolay.grozev
